      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA SHINE (7) boasts a strong record this course with two wins and two minors from five tries. Hit the frame latest (17.92) when third at Richmond Straight in a Mix 1/2/3. Has the ability and should feature. TRUNKEY CHIEF (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at Gosford in a handy 22.17 beating Good Odds Turbo. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Likely to be in the finish. NO MORE TROUBLE (2) missed the frame last time at Wentworth Park but was in the finish the start prior when eighth (18.88) and goes well this course. Can turn it around this time. BATGIRL (3) raced handy last time and scored. Sure to run well again.",
